original: DURLING, Tore Jakob, Civilingenjör, Avesta, f Forsby, Skarab l, 15/4 86 av godsäg J A D o Anna Otterström, gm Karin Hennerberg. Studex 04, ex KTH 09. Gjuteriing v Avesta Jernverks AB. Stdsflm sed. 31, led av beredn.-utsk o drätselkamm 31—43. Ordf i Avesta stads folkskolebyggn.kté, ordf i Södra Dalarnas Tekn Frn.
translated: DURLING, Tore Jakob, Civil Engineer, Avesta, born in Forsby, Skaraborg County, on April 15, 1886, son of estate owner J.A. Durling and Anna Otterström, married to Karin Hennerberg. Received high school diploma in 1904, graduated from the Royal Institute of Technology in 1909. Worked in casting engineering at Avesta Jernverks AB. Served in various administrative committees and boards from 1931 to 1943. Chairman of the Avesta city's elementary school building committee, chairman of the Southern Dalarna Technical Association.
